  "output_log": [
    "Old Maren stoops beside her baskets, sorts out the basics in practiced order, and presses them into your hands one piece at a time.",
    "Thread your catch onto this if you plan to keep fishing.",
    "Old Maren says, \"Start with the pole, then mind your bait. I've set you up with fishing pole, fish string, hook, line, worm.\"",
    "You bait your hook with worm.",
    "You cast your line into the water.",
    "You wait for a bite...",
    "There is a sodden drag on the line, like something dead and heavy below the surface.",
    "RETURN None",
    "You pull something unexpected from the water...",
    "A little trinket flashes once beneath the water before you land it.",
    "Old Maren counts out 9 coppers. \"Lucky pull. Someone will pay for that.\"",
    "You bait your hook with worm.",
    "You cast your line into the water.",
    "You wait for a bite...",
    "Your line jerks violently -- this is no fish.",
    "RETURN None",
    "Whatever it was tears free, snapping your line.",
    "You feel your outdoorsmanship settling into dabbling.",
    "You rig the pole and set the hook and line in order."
  ],
